title: To Stir Up an Ornate Nest
description: To Stir Up an Ornate Nest is a poetic kaleidoscope of human emotions and experiences. It is a keen insight on issues ranging from India's patriarchal psyche, society's tenacious beliefs, lessons learnt from nature, to the oft missed subtleties of life's daily joys and struggles.
author: Shubhangi Joshi
